{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2f81ffcfca","title":"浙江大学关于民主选举问题的大字报","origin":"浙江大学马列主义教研室资料室编印《右派言论汇编（内部刊物）》，1957年11月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e035f644ee","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"2f81ffcfca"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"31a5cbc21a","type":"title","text":"浙江大学关于民主选举问题的大字报","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"cdca52c674","type":"subtitle","text":"1、代表是派出来的（标题为编者所加）","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"b483e45e95","type":"paragraph","text":"人民代表应谁选？！我校杭市代表范正翘，大家知道不知道？？？范正翘当代表，我们一点不知道，人民代表那里来，党委会里面派出来；民主作风何去了，领导塞进腰包中，任命代替民主选，官僚宗派加教条，吁嗟嗟！","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"cc01d1390a","type":"paragraph","text":"此情此景已成习，何日方能挖此根？！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"359f9c94c0","type":"paragraph","text":" 三舍\t204室\t206室","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"af511086f7","type":"subtitle","text":"2、“任命”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"1bc7888061","type":"paragraph","text":"选不上班长可当系主席，机三总支委落选后仍能任职，没有群众基础的郭永健可笑的还要把他送到莫斯科。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"0a27f03568","type":"paragraph","text":"“我们不愿做选举机器，难道大学生只会画圈圈吗”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"7379c7b2e6","type":"paragraph","text":"“我们要求有职有权的学生会——能代表全体同学的学生会，不要缩手缩脚，当尾巴”。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"c3a71e699a","type":"paragraph","text":"[郭永健是浙大学生会主席，杭州市学联主席，今年曾赴苏参加世界青年联欢节。--编者注]","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"04a276e005","type":"subtitle","text":"3、摇篮民主","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"1a24b2b232","type":"paragraph","text":"共产党给我们带来了民主，可是浙大的民主，尚处在摇篮时期，好心的领导，替同学考虑得太周到了，以范正翘什么时候选上了人民代表，同学一个也不知道。据布告郭永健作为中国青年出席世界青年联欢节的代表，我们很奇怪，这样算是代表吗？例如说领导上任命为XX长还来得名顺些。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"64887783e9","type":"paragraph","text":"我们不了解领导为什么这样不信任同学，为什么不让同学选择自己熟悉的候选人，无论学生会、团委体协选举，总是指定几个人叫大家画“??”我们都是经党的多年培养教育的青年，难道非得扶着我们来享受民主权利。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"6a8649b956","type":"subtitle","text":"4、号外","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"31deefd788","type":"paragraph","text":"郭永健即将去莫斯科了！！！真难道让他去做我们的“代表”！不！我们全力支持电器543等班的呼吁，立即撤销毫无群众基础，充满官僚习气的郭永健的代表资格，要求学生会采取措施，我们迫切需要全体同学支持！","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"e28419fdff","type":"paragraph","text":"[按：中华全国学联来信给郭永健（来信不详）]","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"163dcd660f","type":"paragraph","text":" 电制三\t一群同学","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"e0a866a57d","type":"subtitle","text":"5、如此","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"f84bcc55da","type":"paragraph","text":"化工系“民主选举”真令人莫名惊诧！","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"de1775f80e","type":"paragraph","text":"连画圈圈点将法的选举也捞不到","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"b471c9c48d","type":"paragraph","text":"苦哉！苦哉！","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"596bafbaf8","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们怨声载道，怪那个系付主席小官僚，岂知他稳稳连任不肯跑，怪哉！怪哉！","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"501dbe49f2","type":"subtitle","text":"6、我们要民主","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"51024173c1","type":"paragraph","text":"学生会是我们自己的组织，但遗憾的是候选人的名单竟要团委、党委“看过”这是不是体现党委的领导？！我们要求的是——真正能代表自己的学生会。","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"9faabd684b","type":"paragraph","text":"系会系会——何处来，","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"33cb081df4","type":"paragraph","text":"电机系有一个系会，但奇怪的是连学生会代表也不知道它是那里来的。","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"},{"id":"555798b8dd","type":"paragraph","text":"它能代表谁？！","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca"}],"page":{"id":"7e56fa621d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2f81ffcfca","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}